title: Matters of principle: "Innocent until proven guilty".
description: In the context of reckless accusations, threats of violence, etc. (within "the vegan community" in Chiang Mai that I hear so much about), here are some reflections on the importance of skepticism, tolerance, and presuming that people are innocent until proven guilty.
